data.title: Diocese of Rarotonga, Cook Islands
data.meta_description: The bishop is Bishop Reynaldo Bunyi Getalado, M.S.P., who succeeded on 29 June 2024.
data.text:
Bishop of Rarotonga (Cook Islands) (2011.04.11 – 2024.06.29)

President of Episcopal Conference of the Pacific (2016.09 – 2023.11)

Priest of Auckland (New Zealand) (1962.06.30 – 1977.03.21)

Bishop of Rarotonga (Cook Islands) (1977.03.21 – 1983.06.06)

Bishop of Auckland (New Zealand) (1983.06.06 – 1994.12.19)

Bishop of Hamilton (New Zealand) (1994.12.19 – 2014.11.22)

President of Federation of Catholic Bishops’ Conferences of Oceania (2002 – 2006)

President of New Zealand Catholic Bishops Conference (2003.11 – 2009.09)
